uth-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">在南美举行的广泛巡回演出</a>之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">，澳大利亚举行了更多音乐会</a>。</p><p>在其他利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）新闻中，这位音乐家最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-thousands-oasis-tickets-cancelled-speaks-out-on-special-guests-3836620">在绿洲聚会的数千张门票被Ticketmaster取消后发表了回应</a>。</p><p>然而，尽管为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-partner-with-twickets-for-reunion-tour-3788427">防止吹捧以夸张的价格重新销售其吹捧的努力</a>，但英国节目的门票仍在八月发售，但大约有50,000张门票在转售地点最终出现。作为回应，发起人Live Nation和SJM确认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">通过二级售票网站出售的所有门票将被取消</a>，并通过Ticketmaster以面值再次提供。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800092" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800092" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800092" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg" alt="绿洲的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800092" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis的Liam和Noel Gallagher。学分：西蒙·埃米特（Simon Emmett）</figcaption></figure><p>但是，这一过程远非